---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use - Replaid" description="Read the terms and conditions for using the Replaid service.">
  <Header />
  <main class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="mono-label mb-4">Legal</div>
        <h1 class="text-display-sm font-bold mb-4">Terms of Use</h1>
        <p class="text-ink-300">Last updated on March 19, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>Please read these Terms and Conditions ("Terms", "Terms and Conditions", "Terms of Use") carefully before using the REPLAID.pro website (the "Service") operated by Replaid ("us", "we", or "our").</p>

        <p>By accessing or using the Service you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you disagree with any part of the terms then you may not access the Service.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Code of Conduct</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-ink-200">
          <li>No illegal activities</li>
          <li>No fraud</li>
          <li>No spam and data mining</li>
          <li>No exploitation</li>
          <li>No impersonation</li>
          <li>No activities related to bots</li>
          <li>No use other than the intended</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Any violation to these rules means the deletion of your account and associated data. Whether conduct violates our Code of Conduct will be determined in Replaid's sole discretion.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Age Restriction</h3>
        <p>The platform is available for any 18 years old user or older. If you are between 13 and 18 years old, you can still use the Platform but you must have your parents or guardian's permission.</p>
        <p>If you are under 13 years old, you may not use our Platform in any manner.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p>The content on the Platform, including all information, software, technology, data, logos, marks, designs, text, graphics, pictures, audio and video files, and their selection and arrangement, is referred to as "Replaid Content", and is and remains the sole property of Replaid. Replaid Content may not be modified by you in any way.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Account Ownership</h3>
        <p>Replaid has the right to request additional information from You to determine account ownership. The information that We may request includes a copy of Your photo ID, billing information, and certified copies of tax forms.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Refund Policy</h3>
        <p>We are confident in the value that Replaid provides. However, if you believe the product did not meet your expectations, you may request a refund for your last billing cycle.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Cancellation and Deletion</h3>
        <p>If You cancel a paid plan, the cancellation will become effective at the end of the then-current billing cycle. You may delete Your account at any time.</p>
        <p>Any account on the free plan may be deleted if it remains inactive for a continuous period of at least six (6) months.</p>
        <p>If Your account is deleted, Your Content may no longer be available and all licenses granted will terminate. Replaid is not responsible for the loss of such content upon deletion.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Errors</h3>
        <p>Replaid does not guarantee that unexpected errors won't appear and system will be accessible 100% of the time although the maximum effort is put into preventing this.</p>
        <p>We reserve the right to amend the Platform, and any service or material we provide on the Platform, in our sole discretion without notice.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Changes to this Policy</h3>
        <p>We reserve the right, at our sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms at any time. If a revision is made we will try to provide at least 30 days notice prior to any new terms taking effect.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-8">Contact</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding this policy, please <a href="mailto:hi@replaid.pro" class="text-accent hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
